907
01:06:28.359 --> 01:06:30.329
<i>Aku ingin bertemu Geon Young.</i>

908
01:06:36.669 --> 01:06:38.109
<i>Sampai jumpa.</i>

909
01:06:38.109 --> 01:06:39.268
<i>Ya.</i>

910
01:06:40.838 --> 01:06:41.838
<i>Ayo.</i>

911
01:07:08.039 --> 01:07:12.138
